"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:26:54.000Z","msg":"由細都覺得呢個故仔俾鬼佬用黎講咩孝義同勇敢係好怪，明明就打仗打到要強徵老人上戰場又要盲從軍隊攞條命出去博，仲攞呢個故仔黎做商業電影其實好撚cultural misappropriation，唔通我話個故仔營造中國女性形象係盲從權力係今日社會係件好事咩"},{"pid":"8bcca28dd5b85921f4dbe375949c6651d704e400","tid":1923882,"uid":19437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:28:50.000Z","msg":"手足Enzo mazak 都有幫手。無停過手。大家記得多謝埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24113b5922e42643e2caee8a45b6a0dd154a98b3","tid":1923882,"uid":173844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:38:57.000Z","msg":"浪費時間睇垃圾戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1943b650da2534f84a89f331f6226d2f9202a1d8","tid":1923882,"uid":340729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:40:24.000Z","msg":"睇你老鼠《男人婆》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇頭條新聞啦<br />\n<br />\n頭條新聞:港台電視31 逢每周五晚20:00 我要半個熱門都睇到<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1923953\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1923953</a>"},{"pid":"c09ec621ed10d9eab68b01afa6fb2fe412c77fcd","tid":1923882,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:51:06.000Z","msg":"都唔知有乜咁開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家上蝕到入肉先係嘛<br />\n延遲上佢咪有機會賺到錢？<br />\n有人喺佢上之前放左上網就真係要小鳳姐喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8680dc5acce9ed9803448bf6e17f4425f7021db9","tid":1923882,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:59:38.000Z","msg":"唔好打飛機<br />\n係全球武漢肺炎爆發 無人去睇戲先延遲上"},{"pid":"319d9501a3e55294406f82d8825d1dfbea2b12a2","tid":1923882,"uid":342828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T12:02:20.000Z","msg":"最好留番將來佢同D孫一齊去睇首映。"}]}